@prefix : <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-security#> .
@prefix bs: <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-core#> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

<https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-security>
  a owl:Ontology ;
  owl:imports <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-core> ;
  rdfs:label "ByteStar Security & PQC" ;
  rdfs:comment "PQC tiering (hot/warm/cold), receipts, ZK proofs, KEM settlement." .

### PQC operations & tiering
:PQCOp a owl:Class .
:Verify a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf :PQCOp .
:Sign a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf :PQCOp .
:KeyGen a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf :PQCOp .

:placement a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :PQCOp ; rdfs:range xsd:string .
# Values: "hot" | "warm" | "cold"

:targetLatencyNs a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :PQCOp ; rdfs:range xsd:decimal .
:batchSize a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :PQCOp ; rdfs:range xsd:integer .

### Rolling receipts (BLAKE3)
:Receipt a owl:Class .
:BLAKE3 a owl:Class ; rdfs:subClassOf :Receipt .
:rollsInto a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :Receipt ; rdfs:range :Receipt .
:seals a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :Receipt ; rdfs:range bs:Crystal .
:digest a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :Receipt ; rdfs:range xsd:hexBinary .

### Zero-knowledge proofs
:ZKProof a owl:Class .
:constantSchedule a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :ZKProof ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .
:noSecretBranching a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :ZKProof ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .
:proves a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :ZKProof ; rdfs:range bs:Crystal .

### KEM (Key Encapsulation Mechanism)
:KEM a owl:Class .
:encapsulates a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain :KEM ; rdfs:range bs:Crystal .
:privateSettlement a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :KEM ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .